Ruggedman | Track cover art Nigerian rapper Ruggedman has released a new single “Change” off his forth coming Ep titled “The Situation”. The Ep is to contain songs that speak about things happening in the country and the world at large. On change , Ruggedman touches on issues plaguing the country. The new song “Change” was produced by Seanz Beatz and features the young and talented Specikinging. It was mixed and mastered by Marqaimixx. The track is out on all digital music platforms. Click https://linktr.ee/Ruggedman to listen Ruggedman hosts the tv show “What’s Happening With Ruggedman” and the radio show “Wetin Dey With Ruggedman” where he discusses his topics and trends.